The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | 3 held for phone theft 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       3 held for phone theft 
          A STAFF REPORTER                              
	Three youths were arrested on Thursday on the charge of stealing cellphones and LCD monitors from a shop on Lenin Sarani last month.        
	Two LCD monitors and 24 cellphones were seized from them.        
	A probe is on to find out whether the trio  Sauqat Mollah, 18, Mohammad Rajesh, 19, and Sydul Mollah, 24,  are part of an organised gang. They had stolen 50 handsets, an iPod and four LCD monitors from the shop on September 24.                                                                                                                                                                          
